Package game

Contains classes that have to do with the actual game of Cards Against Humanity itself.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CAH_Game
    A class of object that represents a Cards Against Humanity game.
    Rules
    A class of object that represents a set of rules for a CAH game without House Rules.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    CAH_Game.Phases
    A list of different phases that a game of CAH can be in.
    GameTypes
    A list of different types of games.
    HouseRules
    A list of the types of house rules that may be applied to CAH.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    CardNotFoundException
    An exception that is thrown when a card is not found in the array answer in CAH_GameComponents
    PlayerNotFoundException
    A class of object that represents an exception that is thrown when a player is not found.
    RuleConflictException
    An exception that is thrown when there is a rule conflict.
